amily: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-3-configure-the-spring-controller\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/spring-annotation-webconfig.html#3-configure-the-spring-controller\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>3. Configure the Spring Controller</h3><div class=\"highlight highlight-java\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">				<span class=\"pl-k\" style=\"color: rgb(167, 29, 93);\">package</span> <span class=\"pl-smp\">com.prapps.tutorial.spring.controller</span>;\n\n<span class=\"pl-k\" style=\"color: rgb(167, 29, 93);\">import</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">org.springframework.stereotype.Controller</span>;\n<span class=\"pl-k\" style=\"color: rgb(167, 29, 93);\">import</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.RequestMapping</span>;\n\n@<span class=\"pl-stj\">Controller</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s\" style=\"color: rgb(167, 29, 93);\">public</span> <span class=\"pl-s\" style=\"color: rgb(167, 29, 93);\">class</span> <span class=\"pl-en\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">IndexController</span> {\n\n    <span class=\"pl-st\" style=\"color: rgb(167, 29, 93);\">@RequestMapping</span>(<span class=\"pl-c1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 179);\">value</span><span class=\"pl-k\" style=\"color: rgb(167, 29, 93);\">=</span><span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>/<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>)\n    <span class=\"pl-s\" style=\"color: rgb(167, 29, 93);\">public</span> <span class=\"pl-stj\">String</span> <span class=\"pl-en\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">index</span>() {\n        <span class=\"pl-k\" style=\"color: rgb(167, 29, 93);\">return</span> <span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>index<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>;\n    }\n}</pre></div><hr style=\"height: 4px; margin: 16px 0px; overflow: hidden; border-top-width: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; background: rgb(231, 231, 231);\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-4-create-an-index-page-to-test-the-application\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/spring-annotation-webconfig.html#4-create-an-index-page-to-test-the-application\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>4. Create an index page to test the application.</h3><div class=\"highlight highlight-html\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">&lt;%@ page language=\"java\" contentType=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\"\n    pageEncoding=\"UTF-8\"%&gt;\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC <span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\">\"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN\"</span> <span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\">\"http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd\"</span>&gt;\n&lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">html</span>&gt;\n&lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">head</span>&gt;\n&lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">meta</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">http-equiv</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>Content-Type<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">content</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>text/html; charset=UTF-8<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>&gt;\n&lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">title</span>&gt;Index&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">title</span>&gt;\n&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">head</span>&gt;\n&lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">body</span>&gt;\nWelcome !\n&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">body</span>&gt;\n&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">html</span>&gt;</pre></div><hr style=\"height: 4px; margin: 16px 0px; overflow: hidden; border-top-width: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; background: rgb(231, 231, 231);\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-5-done-\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/spring-annotation-webconfig.html#5-done-\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>5. Done !!!</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Deploy the application on server and type the following url http://localhost:8080/spring-java-webconfig/&nbsp;<br><img src=\"https://github.com/pratik006/tutorials/raw/master/spring/annotated-web-config/docs/Screenshot.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Screenshot\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></p><hr style=\"height: 4px; margin: 16px 0px; overflow: hidden; border-top-width: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; background: rgb(231, 231, 231);\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-conclusion\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/spring-annotation-webconfig.html#conclusion\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>Conclusion</h3><p style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">So we find that configuring Spring based Web Application even without a web.xml or any xml configuration file is quite easy. Spring also allows configuring JPA EntityMangagerFactory without a persistence.xml which is covered&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/pratik006/tutorials/wiki/Spring-Complete-Annotation-Based-Config\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">here.</a></p></div>','','2015-12-06 00:24:22','Pratik Sengupta','Spring Complete Annotation Based Config','2015-12-06 00:24:22','Pratik Sengupta',NULL,NULL),(12,'<p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Google Guice is an open source software framework which provides support for dependency injection using annotations to configure Java objects.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Following is an example for beginners. Source code for this can be downloaded at the end of this tutorial.</p><hr style=\"height: 4px; margin: 16px 0px; overflow: hidden; border-top-width: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; background: rgb(231, 231, 231);\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-1-add-dependencies\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice.html#1-add-dependencies\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>1. Add dependencies</h3><hr style=\"height: 4px; margin: 16px 0px; overflow: hidden; border-top-width: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; background: rgb(231, 231, 231);\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">File : pom.xml</p><div class=\"highlight highlight-xml\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">&lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">project</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">xmlns</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> \n    <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">xmlns</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">:</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">xsi</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>\n    <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">xsi</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">:</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">schemaLocation</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 </span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\">    http://maven.apache.org/maven-v4_0_0.xsd<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>&gt;\n  &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">modelVersion</span>&gt;4.0.0&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">modelVersion</span>&gt;\n  &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;com.prapps.tutorial&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;\n  &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;google-guice&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;\n  &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">packaging</span>&gt;jar&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">packaging</span>&gt;\n  &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;1.0.0-SNAPSHOT&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;\n  &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">name</span>&gt;google-guice&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">name</span>&gt;\n  &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">url</span>&gt;http://maven.apache.org&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">url</span>&gt;\n\n  &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependencies</span>&gt;\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;log4j&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;log4j&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;1.2.17&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;\n        &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;junit&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;junit&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;4.11&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;\n        &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;com.google.inject&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;guice&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;3.0&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;\n        &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n    &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependencies</span>&gt;\n&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">project</span>&gt;</pre></div><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-2-create-the-project-structure\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice.html#2-create-the-project-structure\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>2. Create the project structure</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/resources/images/tutorials/project_structure-google-guice.png\" alt=\"project structure\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-3-vo-class\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice.html#3-vo-class\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>3. VO class</h3><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">		<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice.vo;\n\npublic class Employee {\n\n    private long id;\n    private String name;\n    private double salary;\n\n    public long getId() {\n        return id;\n    }\n    public void setId(long id) {\n        this.id = id;\n    }\n    public String getName() {\n        return name;\n    }\n    public void setName(String name) {\n        this.name = name;\n    }\n    public double getSalary() {\n        return salary;\n    }\n    public void setSalary(double salary) {\n        this.salary = salary;\n    }\n}\n</code>\n	</pre><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-4-service-interface\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice.html#4-service-interface\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>4. Service Interface</h3><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">		<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice.service.api;\n\nimport java.util.Collection;\n\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.vo.Employee;\n\npublic interface EmployeeService {\n\n    void addEmployee(Employee employee);\n\n    Collection&lt;Employee&gt; searchEmployeeByName(String name);\n\n    Employee searchEmployeeById(Long id);\n}\n</code>\n	</pre><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-5-serviceimpl-class\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice.html#5-serviceimpl-class\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>5. ServiceImpl class</h3><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">		<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice.service.impl;\n\nimport java.util.ArrayList;\nimport java.util.Collection;\nimport java.util.HashMap;\nimport java.util.Map;\nimport java.util.Map.Entry;\n\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.service.api.EmployeeService;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.vo.Employee;\n\npublic class EmployeeServiceImpl implements EmployeeService {\n\n    private Map&lt;Long, Employee&gt; employeeMap = new HashMap&lt;Long, Employee&gt;();\n\n    public void addEmployee(Employee employee) {\n        employeeMap.put(employee.getId(), employee);\n    }\n\n    public Collection&lt;Employee&gt; searchEmployeeByName(String name) {\n        Collection&lt;Employee&gt; result = new ArrayList&lt;Employee&gt;();\n        for(Entry&lt;Long, Employee&gt; entry : employeeMap.entrySet()) {\n            if(entry.getValue().getName().equals(name)) {\n                result.add(entry.getValue());\n            }\n        }\n        return result;\n    }\n\n    public Employee searchEmployeeById(Long id) {\n        return employeeMap.get(id);\n    }\n\n}\n</code>\n	</pre><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-6-logger-class\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice.html#6-logger-class\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>6. Logger class</h3><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">		<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice.aop;\n\nimport org.aopalliance.intercept.MethodInterceptor;\nimport org.aopalliance.intercept.MethodInvocation;\nimport org.apache.log4j.Logger;\n\npublic class LogAspect implements MethodInterceptor {\n\n    private static final Logger LOG = Logger.getLogger(LogAspect.class);\n\n    public Object invoke(MethodInvocation invocation) throws Throwable {\n        LOG.trace(invocation.getMethod());\n        if(null != invocation.getArguments() &amp;&amp; invocation.getArguments().length &gt; 0) {\n            for(Object arg : invocation.getArguments()) {\n                LOG.trace(arg.getClass() + \" -- \" + arg);\n            }\n        }\n        Object response = invocation.proceed();\n        LOG.trace(response);\n        return response;\n    }\n\n\n}\n</code>\n	</pre><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-7-injector-class\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice.html#7-injector-class\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>7. Injector class</h3><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">		<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice.ioc;\n\nimport com.google.inject.AbstractModule;\nimport com.google.inject.Singleton;\nimport com.google.inject.matcher.Matchers;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.aop.LogAspect;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.service.api.EmployeeService;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.service.impl.EmployeeServiceImpl;\n\npublic class EmployeeAppInjector extends AbstractModule {\n\n    @Override\n    protected void configure() {\n        bind(EmployeeService.class).to(EmployeeServiceImpl.class).in(Singleton.class);\n        LogAspect logAspect = new LogAspect();\n        requestInjection(logAspect);\n        bindInterceptor(Matchers.subclassesOf(EmployeeService.class), Matchers.any(), logAspect);\n    }\n}\n</code>\n	</pre><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-8-tester-class\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice.html#8-tester-class\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>8. Tester class</h3><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">		<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice;\n\nimport java.util.Collection;\n\nimport org.junit.Before;\nimport org.junit.Test;\n\nimport com.google.inject.Guice;\nimport com.google.inject.Injector;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.ioc.EmployeeAppInjector;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.service.api.EmployeeService;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.vo.Employee;\n\npublic class Tester {\n\n    private EmployeeService employeeService; \n\n    @Before public void setUp() {\n        Injector injector = Guice.createInjector(new EmployeeAppInjector());        \n        employeeService = injector.getInstance(EmployeeService.class);\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    public void testAddEmployee() {\n        Employee employee = new Employee();\n        employee.setId(101l);\n        employee.setName(\"Souvik Majumder\");\n        employee.setSalary(1234.0d);\n        employeeService.addEmployee(employee);\n\n        employee = new Employee();\n        employee.setId(102l);\n        employee.setName(\"Pratik Sengupta\");\n        employee.setSalary(4321.0d);\n        employeeService.addEmployee(employee);\n\n        employee = new Employee();\n        employee.setId(103l);\n        employee.setName(\"Debojit Chatterjee\");\n        employee.setSalary(8675.0d);\n        employeeService.addEmployee(employee);\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    public void testSearchEmployee() {\n        testAddEmployee();\n\n        Employee employee = employeeService.searchEmployeeById(101l);\n        assert(\"Souvik Majumder\".equals(employee.getName()));\n        assert(1234d == employee.getSalary());\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    public void testSearchEmployeeByName() {\n        testAddEmployee();\n\n        Collection&lt;Employee&gt; employees = employeeService.searchEmployeeByName(\"Pratik Sengupta\");\n        assert(1 == employees.size());\n\n        Employee employee = employees.iterator().next();\n        assert(\"Pratik Sengupta\".equals(employee.getName()));\n        assert(4321d == employee.getSalary());\n    }\n}\n</code>\n	</pre><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-6-log4jxml\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice.html#6-log4jxml\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>6. Log4j.xml</h3><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">		<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?&gt;\n&lt;!DOCTYPE log4j:configuration SYSTEM \"log4j.dtd\"&gt;\n&lt;log4j:configuration debug=\"true\"\n                     xmlns:log4j=\'http://jakarta.apache.org/log4j/\'&gt;\n\n   &lt;appender name=\"consoleAppender\" class=\"org.apache.log4j.ConsoleAppender\"&gt;\n      &lt;layout class=\"org.apache.log4j.PatternLayout\"&gt;\n         &lt;param name=\"ConversionPattern\" value=\"%d{dd MMM yyyy HH:mm:ss} %5p %c{1} - %m%n\"/&gt;\n      &lt;/layout&gt;\n   &lt;/appender&gt;\n\n   &lt;appender name=\"fileAppender\" class=\"org.apache.log4j.RollingFileAppender\"&gt;\n      &lt;param name=\"append\" value=\"false\"/&gt;\n      &lt;param name=\"file\" value=\"out/learning.log\"/&gt;\n      &lt;layout class=\"org.apache.log4j.PatternLayout\"&gt;\n         &lt;param name=\"ConversionPattern\" value=\"%d{ABSOLUTE} %-5p [%c{1}] %m%n\"/&gt;\n      &lt;/layout&gt;\n   &lt;/appender&gt;\n\n    &lt;logger name=\"com.prapps.tutorial\" additivity=\"false\"&gt;  \n        &lt;level value=\"trace\" /&gt;\n        &lt;appender-ref ref=\"consoleAppender\" /&gt;\n    &lt;/logger&gt; \n\n   &lt;root&gt;\n      &lt;level value=\"INFO\"/&gt;\n      &lt;appender-ref ref=\"consoleAppender\"/&gt;\n      &lt;appender-ref ref=\"fileAppender\"/&gt;\n   &lt;/root&gt;\n\n&lt;/log4j:configuration&gt;\n</code>\n	</pre><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Source Code Available at github:</span><ul style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\"><li>git clone url -&nbsp;<input id=\"gitCloneUrl\" type=\"text\" value=\"https://github.com/pratik006/tutorials.git\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; font-family: Helvetica, arial, freesans, clean, sans-serif, \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 34px; padding: 7px 8px; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 3px; outline: none; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0745098) 0px 1px 2px inset; width: 250px; background-position: 100% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/pratik006/tutorials\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Download Page</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/pratik006/tutorials/tree/master/google-guice\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Browse</a></li></ul>','','2015-12-06 00:51:43','Pratik Sengupta','Google Guice Quick Start Guide','2015-12-06 00:51:43','Pratik Sengupta',NULL,NULL),(13,'<p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">The following sections will get you started with the basic configuration of google-guice with JPA with a complete working example. The source code can be downloaded as well. This is intended for a beginner not for an advanced user.</p><hr style=\"height: 4px; margin: 16px 0px; overflow: hidden; border-top-width: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; background: rgb(231, 231, 231);\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-1-add-dependencies\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice-jpa.html#1-add-dependencies\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>1. Add dependencies</h3><hr style=\"height: 4px; margin: 16px 0px; overflow: hidden; border-top-width: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; background: rgb(231, 231, 231);\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">File : pom.xml</p><div class=\"highlight highlight-xml\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">&lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">project</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">xmlns</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">xmlns</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">:</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">xsi</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">xsi</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">:</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">schemaLocation</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 </span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\">    http://maven.apache.org/maven-v4_0_0.xsd<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>&gt;\n    &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">modelVersion</span>&gt;4.0.0&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">modelVersion</span>&gt;\n    &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;com.prapps.tutorial&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;\n    &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;google-guice-jpa&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;\n    &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">packaging</span>&gt;jar&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">packaging</span>&gt;\n    &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;1.0.0-SNAPSHOT&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;\n    &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">name</span>&gt;google-guice&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">name</span>&gt;\n    &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">url</span>&gt;http://maven.apache.org&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">url</span>&gt;\n\n    &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependencies</span>&gt;\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;log4j&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;log4j&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;1.2.17&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;\n        &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;junit&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;junit&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;4.11&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;\n        &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;com.google.inject&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;guice&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;3.0&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;\n        &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;org.hibernate.javax.persistence&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;hibernate-jpa-2.1-api&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;1.0.0.Final&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;\n        &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;com.h2database&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;h2&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;1.4.185&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;\n        &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;com.google.inject.extensions&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;guice-persist&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;3.0&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;\n        &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;org.hibernate&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;hibernate-core&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;4.3.8.Final&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;\n        &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;org.hibernate&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">groupId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;hibernate-entitymanager&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">artifactId</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;4.3.8.Final&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">version</span>&gt;\n        &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependency</span>&gt;\n\n    &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">dependencies</span>&gt;\n&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">project</span>&gt;</pre></div><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-2-create-the-project-structure\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice-jpa.html#2-create-the-project-structure\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>2. Create the project structure</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/resources/images/tutorials/project_structure-google-guice.png\" alt=\"project structure\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-3-create-the-vo-class\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice-jpa.html#3-create-the-vo-class\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>3. Create the VO class</h3><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice.vo;\n\npublic class Employee {\n\n    private long id;\n    private String name;\n    private double salary;\n\n    public long getId() {\n        return id;\n    }\n    public void setId(long id) {\n        this.id = id;\n    }\n    public String getName() {\n        return name;\n    }\n    public void setName(String name) {\n        this.name = name;\n    }\n    public double getSalary() {\n        return salary;\n    }\n    public void setSalary(double salary) {\n        this.salary = salary;\n    }\n}\n</code></pre><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-4-create-the-entity\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice-jpa.html#4-create-the-entity\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>4. Create the Entity</h3><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice.entities;\n\nimport javax.persistence.Column;\nimport javax.persistence.Entity;\nimport javax.persistence.Id;\nimport javax.persistence.Table;\n\n@Entity\n@Table(name=\"EMPLOYEE\")\npublic class Employee {\n\n    @Id\n    @Column(name=\"ID\")\n    private long id;\n    @Column(name=\"NAME\")\n    private String name;\n    @Column(name=\"SALARY\")\n    private double salary;\n\n    public Employee() {\n        // TODO Auto-generated constructor stub\n    }\n\n    public Employee(long id, String name, double salary) {\n        this.id = id;\n        this.name = name;\n        this.salary = salary;\n    }\n\n    public long getId() {\n        return id;\n    }\n    public void setId(long id) {\n        this.id = id;\n    }\n    public String getName() {\n        return name;\n    }\n    public void setName(String name) {\n        this.name = name;\n    }\n    public double getSalary() {\n        return salary;\n    }\n    public void setSalary(double salary) {\n        this.salary = salary;\n    }\n    @Override\n    public String toString() {\n        return \"Employee [id=\" + id + \", name=\" + name + \", salary=\" + salary + \"]\";\n    }\n\n}\n</code></pre><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-5-add-the-service-interface\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice-jpa.html#5-add-the-service-interface\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>5. Add the Service Interface</h3><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice.service.api;\n\nimport java.util.Collection;\n\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.vo.Employee;\n\npublic interface EmployeeService {\n\n    void addEmployee(Employee employee);\n\n    Collection&lt;Employee&gt; searchEmployeeByName(String name);\n\n    Employee searchEmployeeById(Long id);\n}\n</code></pre><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-6-add-the-dao-interface\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice-jpa.html#6-add-the-dao-interface\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>6. Add the DAO Interface</h3><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice.dao.api;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.entities.Employee;\n\npublic interface EmployeeDao {\n\n    void save(Employee employee);\n    Employee findEmployeeById(long id);\n    List&lt;Employee&gt; findEmployee(String name);\n}\n</code></pre><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-7-service-implementation\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice-jpa.html#7-service-implementation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>7. Service Implementation</h3><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice.service.impl;\n\nimport java.util.ArrayList;\nimport java.util.Collection;\nimport java.util.List;\n\nimport com.google.inject.Inject;\nimport com.google.inject.persist.Transactional;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.dao.api.EmployeeDao;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.service.api.EmployeeService;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.vo.Employee;\n\npublic class EmployeeServiceImpl implements EmployeeService {\n\n    @Inject private EmployeeDao employeeDao;\n\n    @Transactional\n    public void addEmployee(Employee employee) {\n        com.prapps.tutorial.guice.entities.Employee emp = new com.prapps.tutorial.guice.entities.Employee(\n                employee.getId(),\n                employee.getName(),\n                employee.getSalary()\n                );\n        employeeDao.save(emp);\n    }\n\n    public Collection&lt;Employee&gt; searchEmployeeByName(String name) {\n        Collection&lt;Employee&gt; result = new ArrayList&lt;Employee&gt;();\n        List&lt;com.prapps.tutorial.guice.entities.Employee&gt; employees = employeeDao.findEmployee(name);\n        for(com.prapps.tutorial.guice.entities.Employee emp : employees) {\n            result.add(new Employee(emp.getId(), emp.getName(), emp.getSalary()));\n        }\n        return result;\n    }\n\n    public Employee searchEmployeeById(Long id) {\n        com.prapps.tutorial.guice.entities.Employee employee = employeeDao.findEmployeeById(id);\n        Employee empvo = new Employee();\n        empvo.setId(employee.getId());\n        empvo.setName(employee.getName());\n        empvo.setSalary(employee.getSalary());\n        return empvo;\n    }\n\n}\n</code></pre><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">It is important to note that the method&nbsp;<strong>addEmployee</strong>&nbsp;is annotated with&nbsp;<strong>com.google.inject.persist.Transactional</strong>.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-8-dao-implementation\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice-jpa.html#8-dao-implementation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>8. DAO Implementation</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Note: When the DAO class is singleton the entityManager Provider should be used instead of directly injecting the entityManager by @inject EntityManager entityManager as in the later approach every invocation will be a new transaction.</p><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice.dao.impl;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\nimport javax.persistence.EntityManager;\nimport javax.persistence.criteria.CriteriaQuery;\nimport javax.persistence.criteria.Root;\n\nimport org.hibernate.Session;\n\nimport com.google.inject.Inject;\nimport com.google.inject.Provider;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.dao.api.EmployeeDao;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.entities.Employee;\n\npublic class EmployeeDaoImpl implements EmployeeDao {\n\n    @Inject private Provider&lt;EntityManager&gt; emp;\n\n    private Session getSession() {\n        return emp.get().unwrap(Session.class);\n    }\n\n    public Employee findEmployeeById(long id) {\n        return emp.get().find(Employee.class, id);\n    }\n\n    public List&lt;Employee&gt; findEmployee(String name) {\n        /*Criteria criteria = getSession().createCriteria(Employee.class);\n        criteria.add(Restrictions.eq(\"name\", name));\n        return (List&lt;Employee&gt;) criteria.list();*/\n        CriteriaQuery&lt;Employee&gt; createQuery = emp.get().getCriteriaBuilder().createQuery(Employee.class);\n        Root&lt;Employee&gt; root = createQuery.from(Employee.class);\n        createQuery.where(root.get(\"name\").in(name));\n        return emp.get().createQuery(createQuery).getResultList();\n    }\n\n    public void save(Employee employee) {\n        emp.get().merge(employee);\n    }\n}\n</code></pre><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-9-persistencexml\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice-jpa.html#9-persistencexml\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>9. persistence.xml</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">A simple database configuration with H2 database. Note the persistent-unit name should match while installing the JPAPersistModule in the next section.</p><div class=\"highlight highlight-xml\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">&lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">persistence</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">xmlns</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>http://java.sun.com/xml/ns/persistence<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">xmlns</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">:</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">xsi</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>\n    <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">xsi</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">:</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">schemaLocation</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>http://java.sun.com/xml/ns/persistence http://java.sun.com/xml/ns/persistence/persistence_2_0.xsd<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">version</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>2.0<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>&gt;\n    &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">persistence-unit</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>employee-persister<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">transaction-type</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>RESOURCE_LOCAL<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>&gt;\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">provider</span>&gt;org.hibernate.ejb.HibernatePersistence&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">provider</span>&gt;\n\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">class</span>&gt;com.prapps.tutorial.guice.entities.Employee&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">class</span>&gt;\n\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">properties</span>&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">property</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>javax.persistence.jdbc.driver<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>org.h2.Driver<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> /&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">property</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>javax.persistence.jdbc.url<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>jdbc:h2:mem:test<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> /&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">property</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>javax.persistence.jdbc.user<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>sa<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> /&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">property</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>javax.persistence.jdbc.password<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> /&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">property</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>hibernate.dialect<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>org.hibernate.dialect.H2Dialect<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> /&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">property</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>hibernate.hbm2ddl.auto<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>create-drop<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> /&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">property</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>show_sql<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>true<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> /&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">property</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>hibernate.show_sql<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>true<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> /&gt;\n            &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">property</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>hibernate.temp.use_jdbc_metadata_defaults<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>false<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> /&gt;\n        &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">properties</span>&gt;\n    &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">persistence-unit</span>&gt;\n&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">persistence</span>&gt;</pre></div><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-10-start-the-persistence-service\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice-jpa.html#10-start-the-persistence-service\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>10. Start the Persistence Service</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">This class starts the persistence service otherwise it will throw a Null PointerException while accessing database. This can be further configured based on needs.</p><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice.ioc;\n\nimport com.google.inject.Inject;\nimport com.google.inject.Singleton;\nimport com.google.inject.persist.PersistService;\n\n@Singleton\npublic class PersistenceInitializer {\n\n    @Inject\n    PersistenceInitializer(PersistService service) {\n        service.start();\n        // At this point JPA is started and ready.\n    }\n}\n</code></pre><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-11-guice-configuration\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice-jpa.html#11-guice-configuration\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>11. Guice configuration</h3><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice.ioc;\n\nimport com.google.inject.AbstractModule;\nimport com.google.inject.Singleton;\nimport com.google.inject.matcher.Matchers;\nimport com.google.inject.persist.jpa.JpaPersistModule;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.aop.LogAspect;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.dao.api.EmployeeDao;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.dao.impl.EmployeeDaoImpl;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.service.api.EmployeeService;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.service.impl.EmployeeServiceImpl;\n\npublic class EmployeeAppInjector extends AbstractModule {\n\n    @Override\n    protected void configure() {\n        // \"employee-persister\" is defined in the persistence.xml\n        install(new JpaPersistModule(\"employee-persister\"));\n        bind(EmployeeService.class).to(EmployeeServiceImpl.class).in(Singleton.class);\n        bind(EmployeeDao.class).to(EmployeeDaoImpl.class).in(Singleton.class);\n        LogAspect logAspect = new LogAspect();\n        requestInjection(logAspect);\n        bindInterceptor(Matchers.subclassesOf(EmployeeService.class), Matchers.any(), logAspect);\n        bind(PersistenceInitializer.class);\n    }\n}\n</code></pre><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">For deploying in web environments&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 0.2em 0px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0392157);\">filter(\"/*\").through(PersistFilter.class);</code>&nbsp;should be used and PersistenceInitializer is not required.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-12-test-client---add-the-client-to-test-the-configuration\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice-jpa.html#12-test-client---add-the-client-to-test-the-configuration\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>12. Test Client - Add the client to test the configuration</h3><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; white-space: pre; border: 0px; display: inline; max-width: initial; overflow: initial; line-height: inherit; word-wrap: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">package com.prapps.tutorial.guice;\n\nimport java.util.Collection;\n\nimport org.apache.log4j.Logger;\nimport org.junit.Before;\nimport org.junit.Test;\n\nimport com.google.inject.Guice;\nimport com.google.inject.Injector;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.ioc.EmployeeAppInjector;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.ioc.PersistenceInitializer;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.service.api.EmployeeService;\nimport com.prapps.tutorial.guice.vo.Employee;\n\npublic class GuiceTestClient {\n\n    private static final Logger LOG = Logger.getLogger(GuiceTestClient.class);\n    private EmployeeService employeeService; \n\n    @Before public void setUp() {\n        Injector injector = Guice.createInjector(new EmployeeAppInjector());\n        //To start the jpa service add the following line        \n        PersistenceInitializer ps = injector.getInstance(PersistenceInitializer.class);\n        employeeService = injector.getInstance(EmployeeService.class);\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    public void testAddEmployee() {\n        Employee employee = new Employee();\n        employee.setId(101l);\n        employee.setName(\"Souvik Majumder\");\n        employee.setSalary(1234.0d);\n        employeeService.addEmployee(employee);\n\n        employee = new Employee();\n        employee.setId(102l);\n        employee.setName(\"Pratik Sengupta\");\n        employee.setSalary(4321.0d);\n        employeeService.addEmployee(employee);\n\n        employee = new Employee();\n        employee.setId(103l);\n        employee.setName(\"Debojit Chatterjee\");\n        employee.setSalary(8675.0d);\n        employeeService.addEmployee(employee);\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    public void testSearchEmployee() {\n        testAddEmployee();\n\n        Employee employee = employeeService.searchEmployeeById(101l);\n        assert(\"Souvik Majumder\".equals(employee.getName()));\n        assert(1234d == employee.getSalary());\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    public void testSearchEmployeeByName() {\n        testAddEmployee();\n\n        Collection&lt;Employee&gt; employees = employeeService.searchEmployeeByName(\"Pratik Sengupta\");\n        assert(1 == employees.size());\n\n        Employee employee = employees.iterator().next();\n        assert(\"Pratik Sengupta\".equals(employee.getName()));\n        assert(4321d == employee.getSalary());\n        LOG.debug(employee);\n    }\n}\n</code></pre><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-13-log4jxml\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice-jpa.html#13-log4jxml\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>13. Log4j.xml</h3><div class=\"highlight highlight-xml\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.45; padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">&lt;?<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">xml</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\"> version</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>1.0<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\"> encoding</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>UTF-8<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> ?&gt;\n&lt;!<span class=\"pl-k\" style=\"color: rgb(167, 29, 93);\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"pl-v\" style=\"color: rgb(29, 62, 129);\">log4j:configuration</span> SYSTEM \"log4j.dtd\"&gt;\n&lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">log4j</span><span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">:</span><span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">configuration</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">debug</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>true<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>\n                     <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">xmlns</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">:</span><span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">log4j</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\'</span>http://jakarta.apache.org/log4j/<span class=\"pl-pds\">\'</span></span>&gt;\n\n   &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">appender</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>consoleAppender<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">class</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>org.apache.log4j.ConsoleAppender<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>&gt;\n      &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">layout</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">class</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>org.apache.log4j.PatternLayout<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>&gt;\n         &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">param</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>ConversionPattern<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>%d{dd MMM yyyy HH:mm:ss} %5p %c{1} - %m%n<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>/&gt;\n      &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">layout</span>&gt;\n   &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">appender</span>&gt;\n\n   &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">appender</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>fileAppender<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">class</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>org.apache.log4j.RollingFileAppender<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>&gt;\n      &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">param</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>append<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>false<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>/&gt;\n      &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">param</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>file<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>out/learning.log<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>/&gt;\n      &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">layout</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">class</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>org.apache.log4j.PatternLayout<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>&gt;\n         &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">param</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>ConversionPattern<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>%d{ABSOLUTE} %-5p [%c{1}] %m%n<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>/&gt;\n      &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">layout</span>&gt;\n   &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">appender</span>&gt;\n\n    &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">logger</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>org.hibernate<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">additivity</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>false<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>&gt;  \n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">level</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>trace<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> /&gt;\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">appender-ref</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">ref</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>consoleAppender<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> /&gt;\n    &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">logger</span>&gt; \n\n    &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">logger</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">name</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>com.prapps.tutorial<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">additivity</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>false<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>&gt;  \n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">level</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>trace<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> /&gt;\n        &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">appender-ref</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">ref</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>consoleAppender<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> /&gt;\n    &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">logger</span>&gt;\n\n   &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">root</span>&gt;\n      &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">level</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">value</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>INFO<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>/&gt;\n      &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">appender-ref</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">ref</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>consoleAppender<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>/&gt;\n      &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">appender-ref</span> <span class=\"pl-e\" style=\"color: rgb(121, 93, 163);\">ref</span>=<span class=\"pl-s1\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 80, 0);\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>fileAppender<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>/&gt;\n   &lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">root</span>&gt;\n\n&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">log4j</span><span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">:</span><span class=\"pl-ent\" style=\"color: rgb(99, 163, 92);\">configuration</span>&gt;</pre></div><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"user-content-conclusion\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"http://apps-pratiks.rhcloud.com/static/tutorials/google-guice-jpa.html#conclusion\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; display: block; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: -30px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></a>Conclusion</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Point to keep in mind is to start the PersistenceService when using in local environment. For further info please visit&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/google/guice/wiki/JPA\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">https://github.com/google/guice/wiki/JPA</a>&nbsp;and to learn about transactional strategies refer to<a href=\"https://github.com/google/guice/wiki/Transactions\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">https://github.com/google/guice/wiki/Transactions</a></p><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Source Code for this example is available at github:</span><ul style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\"><li>git clone url -&nbsp;<input id=\"gitCloneUrl\" type=\"text\" value=\"https://github.com/pratik006/tutorials.git\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; font-family: Helvetica, arial, freesans, clean, sans-serif, \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 34px; padding: 7px 8px; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 3px; outline: none; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0745098) 0px 1px 2px inset; width: 250px; background-position: 100% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/pratik006/tutorials\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Download Page</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/pratik006/tutorials/tree/master/google-guice-jpa\" style=\"color: rgb(65, 131, 196); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Browse</a></li></ul>','','2015-12-06 00:52:36','Pratik Sengupta','Google Guice with JPA configuration','2015-12-06 00:52:36','Pratik Sengupta',NULL,NULL),(14,'<span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Mul Pokhari, other than being an amazing campsite and a birder’s paradise, also is a gateway to Neora Valley National Park, the last of the few remaining bio-diversities in our country and a UNESCO World Heritage Site. This pristine forest, still largely unexplored, offers protection to more than 31 species of mammals, 250 species of birds, 276 species of insects, and, 38 species of other invertebrates. Many of these are Red Listed according to IUCN. It houses a diverse variety of floras, many of which are extremely rare.</span><div><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\">Day 1:</h3><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Take a night train from Sealdah Railway station to New Jalpaiguri(NJP). There are quite a few trains but Darjeeling Mail and Padatik Express are the most preferred one. We were a group of 20 from TCS-Maitree Adventure Club.We hired tents,sleeping bags,rucksacks and matresses from</span><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; padding-left: 20px;\"><i>Ubac Adventure,&nbsp;<br>34 Mahatma Gandhi Road, Raja Ram Mohan Roy Sarani, Near Purobi Cinema Hall,&nbsp;<br>Kolkata - 700009. Contact No-09038278434.</i></p><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Our train, Darjeeling Mail departed from Sealdah on its scheduled time at 10:30 pm.</span><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\">Day 2:</h3><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">We arrived NJP by 8:00 am in the morning.</span><div class=\"travelImg\" style=\"width: 500px; text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 12px !important;\"><img alt=\"Mt. Khangchendzonga from NJP Rly Stn\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-QpfAiFkyNLg/VLzzJxACg7I/AAAAAAAABp0/vKq4Ld6JKHo/w1190-h894-no/100_8222.JPG\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">Mt. Khangchendzonga from NJP Railway Station</div><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">We had booked a Swaraj Majda which took us to Aritar. On our way we had brunch at Geilkhola along the bank of river Teesta. Most of us enjoyed the freshly steamed Chicken Momos with chilly garlic local made sauce, which awakens my taste buds as I write ! One can enjoy the scenic beauty of river Teesta in Pista color. Locals say that this greenish tinge in the river reflects a clear weather in the mountains. After downpoures the water turns muddy as an aftereffect within 2 days.</span><div class=\"travelImg\" style=\"width: 500px; text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 12px !important;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/wSnOIZjlsIv-G_C04ztlZWSBQbml47obyP5D-aFAQu4=w1192-h894-no\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">River Teesta at Geilkhola</div><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">We ascended to Rangpo along the river Teesta, from here the route turns east towards Rhenok along the Silk Route. we reached Aritar by 3:30 pm. Here we changed for Mulkharkha village, on mahindra comander jeeps through a bumpy and boulder filled roads for which it took us around 45 minutes to reach. One can enjoy the tranquility and serenity of this place with the sun setting in the western horizon creating a golden aura.</span><div class=\"travelImg\" style=\"width: 500px; text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 12px !important;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-yCAp4_l9s-g/VLzqg9btfTI/AAAAAAAABlg/OTjJ934B1Nw/w1190-h894-no/100_8251.JPG\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">Mulkharkha village</div><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">We were welcomed by Mr. Neema Sherpa and his family with tea and pakoras, who shared two of his house as homestay. We were overwhelmed by their hospitality. One must catch the glimpse of sun set at dawn though keeping in mind to return to base before darkness sets in. One must not think that the night life is boring, on contrary it was amazing. They offered us locally fermented drinks,thumba and chang and kept us entertaining with some sentilating local dances and songs. being in a group we enjoyed a lot.</span><div class=\"travelImg\" style=\"width: 500px; text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 12px !important;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-Bj3FBwoJL2U/VMAIYHsjL2I/AAAAAAAABwo/sCoVzQeiSkw/w1192-h894-no/DSCN0281.JPG\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">Our host - Neema Sherpa (at the center)</div><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">our dinner was sumptuous filled with local delicacies consisting of nearby 12 items. All this they do much of to their happiness not as a means of livelihood.We were not at ease with the bone chilling weather except our captain-cum-coordinator,Nilanjanda for whom it was just another day at home. The homestay was a nice experience as the house provided was neat and clean with blankets and quilts. The washroom was common yet well maintained and with ample amount of water. Most of us had a sound sleep.</span><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\">Day 3:</h3><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Witnessing the golden rays illuminating the peak of kanchenjunga was itself a memory.</span><div class=\"travelImg\" style=\"width: 500px; text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 12px !important;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/aGib574rbZIJ1kfsrP6CYTQztu8-DYZ80bJSdi0lVb0=w1192-h894-no\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">Mt. Khangchendzonga (Zoomed)</div><div class=\"travelImg\" style=\"width: 500px; text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 12px !important;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/ZcYqVI59PQdBEuXE3OclsU4U5bKOmircPAGj66dDpmY=w1192-h894-no\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">Mt. Khangchendzonga</div><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">We went to another point from where one can relish the raw beauty of kanchenjunga clearly. We had our breakfast and proceded for mulpokhari,the camping site for the day. At 10:00 am we started our trekking !, We were required to carry drinking water. On the way we witnessed many pictursque views and reached our destination mulpokhari, famous for the wishing lake, within 2 hours. We were unable to witness the reflection of kanchenjunga on the lake as it was covered with clouds but luckily we made it the next day. We pitched our tents for the first time with the initial instruction from our coordinator Nilanjan.</span><div class=\"travelImg\" style=\"width: 500px; text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 12px !important;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-nfCDDmix4tg/VMPmOdYO-jI/AAAAAAAAB-g/exMKTo-jrQc/w1273-h848-no/Nilanjan.jpg\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">Captain cum Mentor - Nilanjan Lahiri</div><div class=\"travelImg\" style=\"width: 500px; text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 12px !important;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-vQcFI-yTuUc/VMAPV_6djmI/AAAAAAAABzI/6dj9e6qwHkM/w1192-h894-no/DSCN0453.JPG\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">Practical lesson on Tent Pitching</div><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">As soon as we were finished with our tent pitching it started drizzling which later turned into snowfall. After having our lunch prepared their only we made it to our shelter and soon the weather cleared. After this we decided to experience and explore the wilderness of Neora Valley National Park,it is also known as birders\' paradise,with our guide. It is the land of the elegant red pandas and rich diverse flaura and fauna making these park an important wilderness zone. one must rfeturn to the base camp before dusk. On the way we collected firewood for the bonfire and witnessed the awe stucking sunset. As time was passing bonfire was the only way to keep us warm against the gradually droppinng temperature. Camp lights, bonfire and torches were the only souce of light.</span><div class=\"travelImg\" style=\"width: 500px; text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 12px !important;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-EbXIW0SKHoY/VMFO10GggvI/AAAAAAAAB5Q/BbVcju0UK98/w1341-h894-no/Fire.jpg\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">Ushnotar khonje (in search of warmth)</div><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Everybody were busy starring at the sky which was flooded with stars! and SHOOTING STARS ! We had dinner under the naked sky with the temperature continously falling and went for the long waited rest.</span><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\">Day 4:</h3><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Ater the sleepless night because of extreme weather conditions we were eagerly waiting for the sunrise yet some where busy snooring. When we were unzipping the tent we realised that everything was frozen from tents to surroundings even ourselves.</span><div class=\"travelImg\" style=\"width: 500px; text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 12px !important;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-mJqX63jk-Co/VL01hqQuKOI/AAAAAAAABrw/pTf-flT6Dcw/w1192-h894-no/IMG_20150118_072824.jpg\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">morning frost</div><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Around 4:30 we witnessed the shimmering beauty of the sky flooded with stars and moon! then we approached to Mulpokhri Wishing Lake to witness the mesmirizing golden rays falling on the \"Khangchendzonga Peak\". The gradual change in the color of the mighty Khangchendzonga from white to orange to white was indeed worth watching. Then we packed our luggages including our tents and started descending to Mulkharkha village. By this time the frost started melting making the mountain slopes very slippery. But luckily it dried off very soon. We reached Mulkharkha Village and were served with the breakfast.</span><div class=\"travelImg\" style=\"width: 500px; text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 12px !important;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-O1eJSqtsWec/VMAOivLKAcI/AAAAAAAABys/3Ha435626bM/w1192-h894-no/DSCN0374-SMILE.jpg\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">On our return journey at Mulkharkha</div><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">The host bid us farewell wholeheartedly in a very tradiotional way by giving scarf and thanking us for being their guest. Though one can reach Aritar by a jeep,which is needed to be booked earlier by informing the host, we trekked down keeping the bag and buggages inside the jeep. We then boarded a bus, which was booked in advance, had lunch at Rangpo and reached NGP at 7:45 pm. We then boarded PADATIK EXPRESS which was scheduled to depart at 9:00 pm and had our dinner which came to us as a surprise by our captain, Nilanjan da while we were busy calling out all the memories.</span><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\">Day 5</h3><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">We reached Sealdah by 7:20 am with new relations, new bondings and new memories of the mesmirizing Mulphokri !</span><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.43; font-size: 1.5em; position: relative; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif;\">Essentials for this Trip</h3><ul style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><li>Sleeping Bag</li><li>Sleeping Mattress</li><li>Trekking/ Walking Shoe</li><li>Cotton Socks</li><li>Sandals or Floaters</li><li>Plate and Spoon (Non “use and throw” please)</li><li>Coffee Mug</li><li>Water Bottle</li><li>Earthen/Natural colored clothes – Jeans is absolutely not recommended</li><li>Warm Clothings (It’s expected to be quite cold at Mul Pokhari)</li><li>Sun Cap</li><li>Rain-coat/ Umbrella</li><li>Personal Medicines, Band Aid, Crepe Bandage, etc.</li><li>Toilet Paper</li><li>Soap/ Soap Paper/ Hand Sanitizer</li><li>Torch Light</li><li>Spare Newspaper</li><li>Spare Plastic Carry Bags</li><li>Photo Id Proof (Both Original and Photocopy)</li><li>Camera</li></ul><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">Note: All photographs in this site are either taken by me or by my friends.</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Segoe UI\', Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br></span></div>','https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-yCAp4_l9s-g/VLzqg9btfTI/AAAAAAAABlg/OTjJ934B1Nw/w1190-h894-no/100_8251.JPG','2015-12-06 01:04:15','Pratik Sengupta','Mesmerizing Mulpokhri - A Camping Experience to cherish','2015-12-06 01:04:15','Pratik Sengupta',NULL,NULL);
